Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=10}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.53,0:01:34.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Novecentos anos atrás...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:36.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Do que você está falando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:40.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you mean a futuristic city\Nlike this existed that many years ago?! - OG}Você está dizendo que uma cidade futurista\Nassim já existia naquela época?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:43.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É apenas uma teoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:47.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A man who once risked\Nhis life for archaeology... - OG}Houve um homem que arriscou\Na vida pela arqueologia...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:50.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{shed light on a certain ancient kingdom. - OG}para desvendar um certo reino antigo.{Polly}
Comment: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:54.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And the manufacture of machinery\Nwhich has been discovered at a certain site... - OG}And... machinery excavated from\Na particular site...{Polly+Camo}
Comment: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:56.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{coincides with the reign of that kingdom. - OG}dates back to that kingdom's reign.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:56.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{And the manufacture of machinery which has been discovered at a certain site... coincides with the reign of that kingdom. - OG}E... maquinário escavado de um local específico\Ndata da era daquele reino.{Polly+Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:04.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Was that machine built\Nduring the Void Century?! - OG}Aquela máquina foi construída\Ndurante o Século Perdido?!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:07.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How much do you know about that? - OG}O quanto você sabe, exatamente?{Polly (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:08.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Hã?\N– Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:11.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Robin! Do you know something?! - OG}Robin! Você sabe sobre isso?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:13.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I bet you don't even want to think back... - OG}Tenho certeza de que é doloroso lembrar...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:17.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but twenty-two years ago,\Nour birthplace, Ohara... - OG}mas vinte e dois anos atrás,\Na sua terra natal, Ohara...{Polly - not sure if OG is a typo or what, but TL (jasmine) confirms that this is, indeed, Vegapunk saying YOUR (as in, Robin's) home. they were not both born there}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:21.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{was destroyed by the Marines' buster call. - OG}foi destruída por um buster call da Marinha.{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.71,0:02:23.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I believe... - OG}Essa é a minha teoria:{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:29.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{that's because Ohara learned\Nof the existence of that kingdom. - OG}Ohara foi destruída porque\Ndescobriu a existência daquele reino.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:34.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Século Perdido...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:38.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{contains the history of the conflict\Nbetween the advanced kingdom - OG}é a história de um conflito entre\Num reino altamente avançado...{Polly+PP+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.81,0:02:41.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and the Twenty Kingdoms. - OG}e uma aliança de vinte reinos.{Polly+T - we're not gonna go with "the" twenty kingdoms unless it becomes apparent later that we need to; as such, "alliance of twenty kingdoms" is more appropriate here}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:53.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Twenty Kingdoms who won the battle... - OG}Esses vinte reinos saíram vitoriosos,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:58.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{later founded the World Government\Nand created the world as we know it. - OG}e fundaram o Governo Mundial,\Ncriando o mundo como o conhecemos hoje.{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:03.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And in order to prevent anyone from\Ninheriting that ancient kingdom's ideology, - OG}Então, para garantir que os ideais\Ndaquele reino nunca fossem transmitidos,{Polly+Camo+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:06.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{they erased it completely from history. - OG}eles o apagaram completamente da história.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't believe it! - OG}O quê...? Isso é insano...!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:12.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! What?! Is that true?! - OG}H-Hã?! Você tá falando sério?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:17.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What an exciting story! - OG}Que história emocionante!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:20.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera aí, Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:23.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If Ohara received a buster call because of that, - OG}Se lançaram um buster call\Nem Ohara por causa disso...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:26.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{that means people who learn about it... - OG}isso quer dizer que quem descobrir...{Polly+T}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, they'll be killed. - OG}É, vão ser eliminados.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:34.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! We didn't even ask!\NWhy did you tell us about it?! - OG}Ei! Por que você contou pra gente?!{Z}{Polly - He seems to only be asking one question in VA anyway, so removed the first one even though "didn't ask" is really funny to say}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:35.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn! - OG}Droga!{Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:38.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've heard it! - OG}Eu ouvi tudo que ele disse!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:40.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've heard it so... - OG}Não dá pra desouvir...{Polly (TCB)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:41.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's forget it! - OG}Hora de esquecer!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:43.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't know anything! - OG}{You don't know anything! - Polly}Eu não sei de nada!{Camo+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I didn't hear a thing! I don't know anything! - OG}Eu não ouvi! Eu não sei de nada!{T+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:48.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I didn't hear a thing! Forget it! - OG}Cabeça vazia! Só esqueçam!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:47.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Se acalmem um pouco.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:50.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I didn't hear anything! Forget it! - OG}Não ouvi nada! Absolutamente nada!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:50.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eu disse que era só uma teoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é horrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não quero morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:57.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, Nico Robin. - OG}Porém, Nico Robin...{PP+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:02.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If Ohara was destroyed\Nbecause of this theory, - OG}se Ohara foi destruída por causa dessa teoria...{PP+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:05.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{don't you think that means the government\Nhas admitted it to be true? - OG}o governo não está basicamente\Nadmitindo que é verdade?{Z+Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:08.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whose side are you on anyway? - OG}De que lado você está, afinal?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:14.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The scholars of Ohara continued to study\Nthe valuable materials and made a theory... - OG}Os estudiosos de Ohara pesquisaram textos\Nhistóricos preciosos para chegar a essa teoria...{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:17.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{With a position as high as yours,\Nwould the government tell you? - OG}O governo não contaria pra alguém\Ncom um cargo tão alto quanto o seu?{Z+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, they didn't tell me anything... - OG}Não, eles não me contaram nada.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The rule still stands. - OG}{The result would be the same. - Polly}É a mesma coisa pra todo mundo.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:25.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even if I'm affiliated with the government,\NI'll be killed if I mention it. - OG}Falar sobre isso resultaria na\Nminha eliminação, independentemente da minha afiliação.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:29.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então eu não quero saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:31.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é tortura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get me out of here! - OG}Me tirem daqui!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:37.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then how did you find out\Nabout the kingdom?! - OG}Então como você descobriu sobre o reino?!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.76,0:04:41.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The books that Ohara acquired\Nfrom all over the world must be... - OG}Todos os livros que Ohara coletou\Nao redor do mundo... estavam...{Polly+T+PP+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:44.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A vontade de Ohara sobrevive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:49.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(3564,0,1,\c&H060610&\3c&H060610&\4c&H060610&)}{That day, the world\Nwas thrown into confusion... - OG}Os eventos daquele dia\Njogaram o mundo no caos.{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:54.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Ohara, an academic island with the most\Nadvanced knowledge in the world, - OG}A ilha dos estudiosos, Ohara,\Ncom o conhecimento mais avançado do mundo,{Polly+T}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:58.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{was destroyed overnight\Nleaving just one girl behind... - OG}foi destruída em um único dia,\Nexceto por uma garotinha...{Polly+PJ - I guess "overnight" is more like the general sentiment, like "Yeah, it felt like it happened overnight." The attack happened during the day, so I think it's better like this}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:04.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ohara was accused of being\Nan evil group of scholars - OG}Os estudiosos foram rotulados\Ncomo um grupo de demônios...{Polly+T+PJ+Z - "Group of devils" seems better to connect more with the usage of "devil" in Enies Lobby as well as Robin's epithet, Devil Child.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:07.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,434)}{plotting to overthrow the World Government. - OG}que buscavam derrubar o Governo Mundial.{Polly}
Comment: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:07.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,434)}Ohara was accused of being an evil group of scholars plotting to overthrow the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alguns meses após o incidente...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu visitei Ohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:19.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Because I knew the late\NProfessor Clover, the archaeologic czar, - OG}Eu conhecia o Professor Clover,\Numa autoridade em arqueologia.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:22.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{so I wanted to lay flowers. - OG}então eu quis deixar flores.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:24.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você o conhecia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele era obcecado pelo Século Perdido...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:35.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and went on adventures to scour\Nthe world for documents about it. - OG}a ponto de sair em aventuras\Npara vasculhar o mundo atrás de textos relacionados.{Polly+PP+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:40.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He was arrested by the Marines,\Nand jailed ten times... - OG}A Marinha o prendeu e o jogou\Nna cadeia nada menos que dez vezes...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.16,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Ali está ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:48.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And he became the most famous\Narchaeologist in the world. - OG}Isso o tornou o arqueólogo\Nmais famoso do mundo.{Polly (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:54.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Eventually, scholars who were impressed\Nby him came together at Ohara, - OG}Com o tempo, a fama de suas façanhas\Natraiu estudiosos para Ohara,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:58.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and the island became\Nthe center for archaeology. - OG}que se tornou um refúgio para a arqueologia.{Polly+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:02.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You can say the tragedy occurred\Nbecause he was talented. - OG}Pode-se dizer que foi o talento dele\Nque causou aquela tragédia.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:06.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando pisei em Ohara,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{the place was an absolute disaster. - OG}o lugar estava em ruínas.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:14.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even the Tree of Knowledge\Nwas burned to the ground, - OG}Até a Árvore do Conhecimento\Nhavia sido queimada até as cinzas...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:17.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and it seemed like everything\Nwas reduced to ashes. - OG}com tudo ao redor reduzido a pó.{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:23.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But when I walked deeper into the island, - OG}Mas conforme eu caminhava para o interior da ilha,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:27.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu presenciei algo surpreendente.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.91,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é tudo isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma enorme quantidade de livros de todos os tipos...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:36.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,estavam submersos no lago\Nno centro da ilha!
Comment: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:36.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A vast amount of books of all kinds... were submerged in the lake at the center of the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:42.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Perhaps the scholars stayed on the island\Nwhich was burning under the buster call, - OG}Eu acredito que os estudiosos resistiram,\Nmesmo enquanto o buster call queimava seu lar,{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:45.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and died protecting the legacy\Nthey were to leave for the future. - OG}e morreram garantindo que seu legado\Nalcançasse o futuro.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:51.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The books that so many scholars\Nprotected at the risk of their lives... - OG}Os livros pelos quais todos aqueles\Nestudiosos arriscaram suas vidas...{Polly+T+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:56.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even if ignorant soldiers found them,\Nthey wouldn't know how valuable they are. - OG}{Even if the Marines found them, ignorant\Nsoldiers wouldn't understand their value. - Polly}Soldados ignorantes da Marinha não entenderiam\No valor deles, mesmo que os encontrassem.{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:06:59.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's a victory for Ohara. - OG}Ohara venceu.{Polly (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{When I saw it, - OG}{When I realized that, - Polly (TCB)}Quando eu vi aquilo,{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:04.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I couldn't stop my tears from falling. - OG}eu não consegui conter as lágrimas.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.28,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, levem a Robin!{Enies 09 - 25:40}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.78,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Minha filha {\i0}precisa{\i1} escapar da ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:10.49,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:12.41,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Não! E a mamãe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.79,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Você não vem comigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:17.29,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Olvia, o que você está...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:21.50,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Ainda tem algo\Nque eu preciso fazer aqui, então...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:25.26,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Mamãe! Não me deixe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:27.01,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou ficar aqui também!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.51,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:31.60,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Como estudiosa de Ohara,\Nvocê deveria entender bem isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:34.27,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,A história é o legado da humanidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:35.14,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Apaguem o fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:36.23,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Protejam os livros!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:38.06,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Salvem o máximo de livros que puderem!{New line}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:40.52,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Joguem os livros pra fora da biblioteca!{New line}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.32,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Ohara não quer expor nossa história.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:46.99,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Nós apenas desejávamos preservar\Nas vozes do passado.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.45,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Nossa pesquisa acaba aqui...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.41,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,mas mesmo que Ohara seja destruída...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:55.58,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,nós não podemos abandonar...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:59.38,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,o futuro da geração de vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.38,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não entendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:06.13,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Você vai entender... um dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:09.47,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:11.51,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,vá, Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:17.44,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem certeza disso?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:19.15,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:23.98,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não quero ir!\NEu quero ficar com você, mamãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:26.86,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Mamãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:30.57,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Viva, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:38.29,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Erga a cabeça, Robin!{Enies 09 - 27:46}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:40.88,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Sua mãe é honrada!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:45.92,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Um dia, transmita a história\Ndesta ilha, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:50.01,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Ohara lutou contra o mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Robin{-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:01.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! How dare you make\Nher cry, you helmet fool! - OG}Ei! Como ousa fazer\Na Robin chorar, seu cabeça de balde!{Polly+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:04.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Unforgivable! Vegapunk! I'll kick you! - OG}Já era, Vegapunk!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:07.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So get these shoes off me, you bastard! - OG}Tira esses sapatos de mim pra eu chutar sua bunda!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:04.90,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{Gee! How insensitive you are! - OG}Você é tão insensível, Vega!{Polly - honestly I kinda want to keep the OG line because it made me laugh so hard... anyway, I think this one is Franky, so...}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:08.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get them off! - OG}Tira logo!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Look at me, you damn helmet! - OG}Olha pra mim, cabeça de balde!{Z+PJ+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:16.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just as you guessed... - OG}É como você pensou.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:23.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ohara descobriu\Na existência daquele reino.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:25.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I see. Then that's a fact. - OG}{I see. Then it's true. - T}Entendo. Então {\i1}é{\i0} verdade.{Polly - not sure which line I like best}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:29.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Where are the books\Nthat were in the lake now? - OG}Onde estão os livros do lago agora?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:32.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu queria levá-los de volta para Punk Hazard,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:35.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but if the higher-ups heard\Nabout it, it would all be over. - OG}{but if they ever discovered\Nthat, it would be over. - Polly}mas não podia arriscar\Nque os superiores descobrissem.{Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:37.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Actually... - OG}Pra falar a verdade...{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:40.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I ran into those guys that day. - OG}Eu encontrei algumas pessoas naquele dia.{PP+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:05.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who is it and what is he doing here? - OG}Quem viria a ruínas como estas?{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Puxa pra cima!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:13.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Giants?! - OG}Gigantes?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why are they doing that? - OG}O que eles estão fazendo?{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:18.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do they know how valuable those books are?! - OG}Eles sabem o valor desses livros?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:20.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os livros...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que eles vão fazer com eles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:25.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It hasn't changed. - OG}Essa sua cabeça...{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:30.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Your head is distinctive.\NI recognized it at first sight. - OG}Tá enorme como sempre. Reconheceria em qualquer lugar.{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:42.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Faz tempo, Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:47.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:52.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Your head has enlarged again. - OG}Sua cabeça cresceu de novo.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Enough about that! - OG}Deixa isso pra lá!{PP+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que você está aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:03.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa é a minha pergunta, Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:07.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I knew the old man Clover. - OG}Eu conhecia o velho Clover.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:10.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What? You, too? - OG}Oh? Você também?{Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:11.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:15.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(3440,0,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}{He used to be a rascal\Ntraveling around the world. - OG}ele costumava ser um desordeiro\Naventurando-se por aí.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:19.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquela bobagem sobre ele\Ntentar destruir o mundo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{is a ridiculous disinformation campaign. - OG}é pura besteira e propaganda!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:29.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Está se perguntando o que eles estão fazendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:33.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't let them take away\Nthose valuable books! - OG}Não posso deixar eles roubarem esses livros valiosos!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:35.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles não são bandidos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:37.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu já verifiquei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:38.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:42.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles vieram de Elbaph.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:45.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles sabem o valor dos livros.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:54.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O capitão deles é um homem estranho\Ncom bandagens por todo o corpo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:59.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He said, "Ohara saved their legacy\Nwhile sacrificing their lives, - OG}Ele disse: "Os oharanos salvaram seu\Nlegado sacrificando suas vidas,{Polly - Jaz pointed out that it can be read a little strangely that "Ohara" sacrificed their lives. Unfortunately this is 16 CPS, but I think it's quite good...}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:03.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e eu não vou deixar isso ser apagado da história."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:15.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm glad that you and your\NWorld Government people... - OG}Ainda bem que vocês\Ndo governo...{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:18.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{didn't find out about this\Nand destroy the books. - OG}não encontraram e destruíram os livros primeiro.{Polly+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:19.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:20.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't do tha– - OG}Eu nunca faria...!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:22.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu achei que fosse brincadeira!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:26.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't believe you finally became\Nthe government's dog. - OG}Não acreditei que você tinha virado\Num cachorrinho do governo.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:31.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{After you turned down our invitation\Nto join the Freedom Fighters. - OG}{Especially after turning down\Nour invitation to the Freedom Fighters. - Polly}E depois de recusar nosso convite\Npara se juntar aos Guerreiros da Liberdade...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:34.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't be a fool! - OG}Não seja idiota!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:37.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even with my wisdom and skills, - OG}Mesmo com meu talento e intelecto,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:40.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{what can I make in a poor army like yours?! - OG}o que eu poderia criar em\Num exército sem recursos como o seu?!{Polly+T+PJ+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I got it. - OG}Entendi.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:46.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're as honest as always. - OG}Você é direto como sempre.{Polly+T}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The World Government is a huge organization. - OG}O Governo Mundial é\Numa organização enorme.{PP+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:52.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There are people who listen\Nto you too, especially in the Marines. - OG}A Marinha, especialmente,\Nestá cheia de pessoas razoáveis.{Z}{Polly - Per TL, Vegapunk seems to be speaking in a more general sense, rather than specifically about listening to Dragon. In other words, it's like saying "You see plenty of reasonable people in the Marines." I think that's what the OG was going for, but this is more accurate.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:55.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't mistake your target, Dragon. - OG}Não perca o objetivo de vista, Dragon.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sei, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:02.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This incident hit me hard. - OG}esse incidente me abalou muito.{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:09.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Harmless scholars who just questioned\Nthe unreasonableness that is the law... - OG}Um grupo de estudiosos inofensivos\Nfoi violentamente eliminado...{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:11.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{were crushed by violence! - OG}simplesmente por questionar essa "lei" absurda!{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:17.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I will build an army that can fight! - OG}Mas eu vou criar\Num exército capaz de revidar!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:20.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But you despised war! - OG}Eu pensei que você detestava guerras!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:22.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aguarde, Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:25.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna change the world! - OG}Eu vou mudar o mundo!{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não vou deixar a morte de Clover...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:31.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and the will of Ohara go in vain! - OG}nem a vontade de Ohara serem em vão!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Naquele mesmo ano, Dragon se juntou a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Emporio Ivankov...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:42.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e Bartholomew Kuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:46.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,para criar o Exército Revolucionário...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{that now rocks the world! - OG}que agora abala o mundo!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:55.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy's dad is so passionate! - OG}{Luffy's dad is so intense! - WF}O pai do Luffy é tão ambicioso!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait a minute! Did you just say Elbaph?! - OG}Espera um segundo! Você disse Elbaph?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:03.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I didn't know Dragon-san and Dr. Clover\Nhad such a relationship! - OG}Eu não sabia que Dragon e o\NProfessor Clover se conheciam...!{Polly+T+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:07.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn Iva... I didn't know he was a founding\Nmember of the Revolutionary Army! - OG}Aquele maldito Iva era um membro fundador\Ndo Exército Revolucionário?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:11.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sinto que minha cabeça vai explodir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:14.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que Kuma nos ajudou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:18.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why did you modify Kuma? Vegapunk! - OG}Por que você o modificou, Vegapunk?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:23.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The books of Ohara certainly should not\Nbe found by the government... - OG}É verdade que o governo\Nnão pode encontrar os livros de Ohara...{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:33.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But I went to Elbaph in secret\Nout of my own interest... - OG}Mas eu fui secretamente a Elbaph\Npor razões pessoais.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And I read all the documents. - OG}Eu li cada documento de lá.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:43.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:46.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,o mistério do mundo\Nque Ohara desvendou...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,vive no meu cérebro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:53.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and I've been working on that research. - OG}e eu tenho continuado a pesquisa deles.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:56.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can I ask you something? - OG}Posso te perguntar uma coisa?{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The name... - OG}Aquele capitão gigante...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{of the Giant captain is... - OG}O nome dele era...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:09.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Saul, isn't it? - OG}Saul, não era?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:15.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He is hiding now. - OG}Ele está escondido agora.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:17.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Preciso manter isso em segredo de todos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:27.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigada, Vegapunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{for not letting the battle\Nof the people of Ohara be in vain. - OG}por não deixar a luta de Ohara\N{be for nothing. - Polly}ser em vão.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:34.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm well versed in all branches of study. - OG}Eu simplesmente sou versado em todas as áreas de estudo.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:36.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o caminho de um verdadeiro estudioso.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:51.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os sapatos estão se movendo sozinhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:16:00.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't release you guys but follow me. - OG}Ainda não posso soltar vocês.\NVão ter que vir comigo.{Polly+T+PP}
Comment: 0,0:15:56.94,0:15:58.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I can't release you guys...
Comment: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:00.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,but follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:03.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem algo que eu quero mostrar a vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:06.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Não tem cabine\Nnessa coisa, Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:10.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh! Maybe this robot... - OG}Já sei! Talvez esse robô...{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:12.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{is autonomous! - OG}se mova sozinho!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:16.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Talvez ele reaja se dissermos algo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:18.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tipo... Tipo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:21.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mova! Mova, robô!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:22.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não funcionou...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{wonder what the magic phrase is... - OG}Qual será a palavra mágica... {Galaxy}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:27.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não! Ele deve ter um nome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:29.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We should call that! - OG}Devemos chamá-lo pelo nome!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mova, Robonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:36.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robo King!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:37.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Gee... - OG}Putz...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês são crianças, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's no way you could\Nget it to work like that. - OG}Obviamente isso não vai funcionar.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:51.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:04.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tá bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What was that?! The robot exploded?! - OG}O que foi isso?! O robô explodiu?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:10.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, não foi uma explosão.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:13.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então o que aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:17.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:20.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me ajudem-{\i1}quasar{\i0}!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:23.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Quasar"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah não!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:25.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Falhei de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:28.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alguém, me ajudem-{\i1}quasar{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:32.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Maybe space-time distorted\Nwhile I was warping! - OG}Talvez eu tenha distorcido o espaço-tempo ao me teletransportar!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele velho já estava ali antes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acho que não.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.41,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Estou afundando! Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:38.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meu corpo tá afundando!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:40.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alguém!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:45.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não sei o que tá acontecendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:48.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Old man, do you need help? - OG}Ei, velhote, precisa de ajuda?{PP+Polly+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me ajudem-{\i1}quasar{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:59.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é igualzinho ao Kin'emon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:04.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:09.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou te tirar daí!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:15.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I thought so! - OG}Eu sabia!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:16.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:19.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:21.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A propósito, você é...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:22.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O filho do Dragon, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sabia que você estava aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:26.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que bom que veio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And... - OG}E você deve ser...{T+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:28.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{you're Bonney! - OG}Bonney!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You've grown up. - OG}Você cresceu tanto!{PP+Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:31.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fico feliz em te ver bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:37.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Velhote, você tá flutuando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:40.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você também tá usando.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:40.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:44.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esses sapatos dom têm uma função de flutuação!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:47.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Função de flutuação?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:48.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How can we use it?! - OG}Como usa?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:52.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Primeiro, aperte o botão na lateral...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, esse aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:57.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E essa alavanca!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:19:00.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Push it further down! - OG}Empurre pra baixo!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:00.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:02.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:13.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We've flown too far! - OG}{We flew too far! - Polly}Voamos alto demais! {Galaxy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:19.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me ajudem-{\i1}quasar{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=11}===============================DIALOGUE============================
